title: We can form a Center-Right Coalition.
subtitle: <span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span> + <span style="color: #63B8FF;">**WBP**</span> + <span style="color: var(--fvp-color);">**[+ fvp_name +]**</span>[? if rlb_exist: + <span style="color: #006400;">**WBWB**</span>?][? if csvd_exist: + <span style="color: #1DB4E1;">**CSVD**</span>?][? if wp_exist: + <span style="color: #B8996F;">**WP**</span>?] ([+ center_right_coalition_wurttemberg +]%)
