@right_coalition_wurttemberg
title: We can form a Right Coalition.
subtitle: <span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #000000;">**Z**</span> + <span style="color: #63B8FF;">**WBP**</span>[? if dnvp_ideology = "Radical": + <span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span>?][? if kswr_exist: + <span style="color: #003755;">**KSWR**</span>?][? if rlb_exist: + <span style="color: #006400;">**WBWB**</span>?][? if csvd_exist: + <span style="color: #1DB4E1;">**CSVD**</span>?][? if wp_exist: + <span style="color: #B8996F;">**WP**</span>?] ([+ right_coalition_wurttemberg +]%)
view-if: right_coalition_wurttemberg > 50
on-arrival: in_right_coalition_wurttemberg = 1; nlp_wurttemberg = 1;
go-to: mp

WIP


@no_majority_wurttemberg
title: There is no clear governing majority.
view-if: weimar_coalition_wurttemberg <= 50 and grand_coalition_wurttemberg <= 50 and bourgeois_coalition_wurttemberg <= 50 and (center_right_coalition_wurttemberg <= 50 or fvp_ideology = "Left") and right_coalition_wurttemberg <= 50 and nlp_wl <= 50
on-arrival: nlp_wurttemberg = 1 if was_nlp_wurttemberg; in_nlp_majority_wurttemberg = 1 if was_in_nlp_majority_wurttemberg; in_weimar_coalition_wurttemberg = 1 if was_in_weimar_coalition_wurttemberg; in_grand_coalition_wurttemberg = 1 if was_in_grand_coalition_wurttemberg; in_bourgeois_coalition_wurttemberg = 1 if was_in_bourgeois_coalition_wurttemberg; in_center_right_coalition_wurttemberg = 1 if was_in_center_right_coalition_wurttemberg; in_right_coalition_wurttemberg = 1 if was_in_right_coalition_wurttemberg;

There is no path to a majority government for now. The current government will stay in power as a minority coalition.





@mp

